{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I'm actually here"},{"time":2000,"text":"to make a challenge to people."},{"time":4000,"text":"I know there have been many challenges made to people."},{"time":7000,"text":"The one I'm going to make"},{"time":9000,"text":"is that it is time for us to reclaim"},{"time":11000,"text":"what peace really means."},{"time":14000,"text":"Peace is not \"Kumbaya, my Lord.\""},{"time":17000,"text":"Peace is not the dove and the rainbow --"},{"time":20000,"text":"as lovely as they are."},{"time":23000,"text":"When I see the symbols"},{"time":25000,"text":"of the rainbow and the dove,"},{"time":27000,"text":"I think of personal serenity."},{"time":30000,"text":"I think of meditation."},{"time":32000,"text":"I do not think"},{"time":34000,"text":"about what I consider to be peace,"},{"time":37000,"text":"which is sustainable peace"},{"time":40000,"text":"with justice and equality."},{"time":43000,"text":"It is a sustainable peace"},{"time":45000,"text":"in which the majority of people"},{"time":48000,"text":"on this planet"},{"time":50000,"text":"have access to enough resources"},{"time":53000,"text":"to live dignified lives,"},{"time":56000,"text":"where these people have enough access"},{"time":59000,"text":"to education"},{"time":61000,"text":"and health care,"},{"time":63000,"text":"so that they can live in freedom from want"},{"time":66000,"text":"and freedom from fear."},{"time":69000,"text":"This is called human security."},{"time":72000,"text":"And I am not a complete pacifist"},{"time":75000,"text":"like some of my really, really heavy-duty,"},{"time":78000,"text":"non-violent friends,"},{"time":80000,"text":"like Mairead McGuire."},{"time":82000,"text":"I understand that humans"},{"time":84000,"text":"are so \"messed up\" --"},{"time":87000,"text":"to use a nice word,"},{"time":89000,"text":"because I promised my mom"},{"time":91000,"text":"I'd stop using the F-bomb in public."},{"time":93000,"text":"And I'm trying harder and harder."},{"time":96000,"text":"Mom, I'm really trying."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"We need a little bit of police;"},{"time":100000,"text":"we need a little bit of military,"},{"time":102000,"text":"but for defense."},{"time":104000,"text":"We need to redefine"},{"time":106000,"text":"what makes us secure"},{"time":108000,"text":"in this world."},{"time":110000,"text":"It is not arming our country"},{"time":112000,"text":"to the teeth."},{"time":115000,"text":"It is not getting other countries"},{"time":117000,"text":"to arm themselves to the teeth"},{"time":119000,"text":"with the weapons that we produce"},{"time":121000,"text":"and we sell them."},{"time":124000,"text":"It is using that money more rationally"},{"time":127000,"text":"to make the countries of the world secure,"},{"time":131000,"text":"to make the people of the world secure."},{"time":135000,"text":"I was thinking about"},{"time":137000,"text":"the recent ongoings"},{"time":139000,"text":"in Congress,"},{"time":141000,"text":"where the president is offering"},{"time":144000,"text":"8.4 billion dollars"},{"time":147000,"text":"to try to get the START vote."},{"time":149000,"text":"I certainly support the START vote."},{"time":151000,"text":"But he's offering 84 billion dollars"},{"time":154000,"text":"for the modernizing"},{"time":157000,"text":"of nuclear weapons."},{"time":159000,"text":"Do you know the figure that the U.N. talks about"},{"time":162000,"text":"for fulfilling the Millennium Development Goals"},{"time":165000,"text":"is 80 billion dollars?"},{"time":170000,"text":"Just that little bit of money,"},{"time":172000,"text":"which to me, I wish it was in my bank account --"},{"time":174000,"text":"it's not, but ..."},{"time":176000,"text":"In global terms, it's a little bit of money."},{"time":181000,"text":"But it's going to modernize weapons"},{"time":183000,"text":"we do not need"},{"time":185000,"text":"and will not be gotten rid of in our lifetime,"},{"time":188000,"text":"unless we get up off our ..."},{"time":190000,"text":"and take action to make it happen,"},{"time":193000,"text":"unless we begin to believe"},{"time":195000,"text":"that all of the things that we've been hearing about"},{"time":197000,"text":"in these last two days"},{"time":199000,"text":"are elements of what come together"},{"time":201000,"text":"to make human security."},{"time":204000,"text":"It is saving the tigers."},{"time":207000,"text":"It is stopping the tar sands."},{"time":210000,"text":"It is having access"},{"time":213000,"text":"to medical equipment"},{"time":215000,"text":"that can actually tell who does have cancer."},{"time":218000,"text":"It is all of those things."},{"time":220000,"text":"It is using our money for all of those things."},{"time":223000,"text":"It is about action."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225000,"text":"I was in Hiroshima"},{"time":227000,"text":"a couple of weeks ago,"},{"time":229000,"text":"and His Holiness --"},{"time":231000,"text":"we're sitting there in front of thousands of people in the city,"},{"time":234000,"text":"and there were about eight of us Nobel laureates."},{"time":236000,"text":"And he's a bad guy. He's like a bad kid in church."},{"time":239000,"text":"We're staring at everybody, waiting our turn to speak,"},{"time":242000,"text":"and he leans over to me, and he says,"},{"time":244000,"text":"\"Jody, I'm a Buddhist monk.\""},{"time":248000,"text":"I said, \"Yes, Your Holiness."},{"time":251000,"text":"Your robe gives it away.\""},{"time":253000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":255000,"text":"He said, \"You know"},{"time":257000,"text":"that I kind of like meditation, and I pray.\""},{"time":260000,"text":"I said, \"That's good. That's good."},{"time":262000,"text":"We need that in the world."},{"time":264000,"text":"I don't follow that, but that's cool.\""},{"time":267000,"text":"And he says, \"But I have become skeptical."},{"time":270000,"text":"I do not believe"},{"time":273000,"text":"that meditation and prayer"},{"time":276000,"text":"will change this world."},{"time":278000,"text":"I think what we need"},{"time":280000,"text":"is action.\""},{"time":282000,"text":"His Holiness, in his robes,"},{"time":284000,"text":"is my new action hero."}]},{"cues":[{"time":287000,"text":"I spoke with Aung Sun Suu Kyi"},{"time":289000,"text":"a couple of days ago."},{"time":291000,"text":"As most of you know,"},{"time":293000,"text":"she's a hero for democracy in her country, Burma."},{"time":296000,"text":"You probably also know"},{"time":298000,"text":"that she has spent 15 of the last 20 years"},{"time":300000,"text":"imprisoned for her efforts"},{"time":303000,"text":"to bring about democracy."},{"time":305000,"text":"She was just released a couple of weeks ago,"},{"time":308000,"text":"and we're very concerned to see how long she will be free,"},{"time":311000,"text":"because she is already out in the streets in Rangoon,"},{"time":313000,"text":"agitating for change."},{"time":315000,"text":"She is already out in the streets, working with the party"},{"time":318000,"text":"to try to rebuild it."},{"time":320000,"text":"But I talked to her for a range of issues."},{"time":323000,"text":"But one thing that I want to say,"},{"time":325000,"text":"because it's similar to what His Holiness said."},{"time":328000,"text":"She said, \"You know, we have a long road to go"},{"time":331000,"text":"to finally get democracy in my country."},{"time":334000,"text":"But I don't believe in hope"},{"time":337000,"text":"without endeavor."},{"time":340000,"text":"I don't believe in the hope of change,"},{"time":343000,"text":"unless we take action"},{"time":345000,"text":"to make it so.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"Here's another woman hero of mine."},{"time":350000,"text":"She's my friend, Dr. Shirin Ebadi,"},{"time":353000,"text":"the first Muslim woman"},{"time":355000,"text":"to receive the Nobel Peace Prize."},{"time":357000,"text":"She has been in exile"},{"time":359000,"text":"for the last year and a half."},{"time":361000,"text":"You ask her where she lives -- where does she live in exile?"},{"time":364000,"text":"She says the airports of the world."},{"time":367000,"text":"She is traveling because she was out of the country"},{"time":370000,"text":"at the time of the elections."},{"time":372000,"text":"And instead of going home,"},{"time":374000,"text":"she conferred with all the other women that she works with,"},{"time":377000,"text":"who said to her, \"Stay out. We need you out."},{"time":380000,"text":"We need to be able to talk to you out there,"},{"time":382000,"text":"so that you can give the message"},{"time":384000,"text":"of what's happening here.\""},{"time":386000,"text":"A year and a half --"},{"time":388000,"text":"she's out speaking"},{"time":390000,"text":"on behalf of the other women in her country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":393000,"text":"Wangari Maathai --"},{"time":395000,"text":"2004 Peace laureate."},{"time":397000,"text":"They call her the \"Tree Lady,\""},{"time":399000,"text":"but she's more than the Tree Lady."},{"time":401000,"text":"Working for peace"},{"time":403000,"text":"is very creative."},{"time":405000,"text":"It's hard work every day."},{"time":407000,"text":"When she was planting those trees,"},{"time":409000,"text":"I don't think most people understand"},{"time":411000,"text":"that, at the same time,"},{"time":414000,"text":"she was using the action"},{"time":416000,"text":"of getting people together to plant those trees"},{"time":419000,"text":"to talk about how to overcome"},{"time":422000,"text":"the authoritarian government in her country."},{"time":425000,"text":"People could not gather"},{"time":427000,"text":"without getting busted and taken to jail."},{"time":430000,"text":"But if they were together planting trees for the environment,"},{"time":433000,"text":"it was okay --"},{"time":435000,"text":"creativity."},{"time":438000,"text":"But it's not just iconic women"},{"time":441000,"text":"like Shirin,"},{"time":443000,"text":"like Aung Sun Suu Kyi, like Wangari Maathai --"},{"time":446000,"text":"it is other women in the world"},{"time":449000,"text":"who are also struggling together"},{"time":451000,"text":"to change this world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453000,"text":"The Women's League of Burma,"},{"time":455000,"text":"11 individual organizations of Burmese women"},{"time":458000,"text":"came together because there's strength in numbers."},{"time":461000,"text":"Working together is what changes our world."},{"time":464000,"text":"The Million Signatures Campaign"},{"time":466000,"text":"of women inside Burma"},{"time":468000,"text":"working together to change human rights,"},{"time":471000,"text":"to bring democracy to that country."},{"time":473000,"text":"When one is arrested and taken to prison,"},{"time":476000,"text":"another one comes out and joins the movement,"},{"time":479000,"text":"recognizing that if they work together,"},{"time":482000,"text":"they will ultimately bring change"},{"time":484000,"text":"in their own country."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486000,"text":"Mairead McGuire in the middle,"},{"time":488000,"text":"Betty Williams on the right-hand side --"},{"time":490000,"text":"bringing peace to Northern Ireland."},{"time":492000,"text":"I'll tell you the quick story."},{"time":494000,"text":"An IRA driver was shot,"},{"time":496000,"text":"and his car plowed into people"},{"time":498000,"text":"on the side of the street."},{"time":500000,"text":"There was a mother and three children."},{"time":502000,"text":"The children were killed on the spot."},{"time":504000,"text":"It was Mairead's sister."},{"time":506000,"text":"Instead of giving in"},{"time":508000,"text":"to grief, depression, defeat"},{"time":511000,"text":"in the face of that violence,"},{"time":514000,"text":"Mairead hooked up with Betty --"},{"time":516000,"text":"a staunch Protestant and a staunch Catholic --"},{"time":519000,"text":"and they took to the streets"},{"time":521000,"text":"to say, \"No more violence.\""},{"time":524000,"text":"And they were able to get"},{"time":526000,"text":"tens of thousands of, primarily, women, some men,"},{"time":529000,"text":"in the streets to bring about change."},{"time":533000,"text":"And they have been"},{"time":535000,"text":"part of what brought peace to Northern Ireland,"},{"time":537000,"text":"and they're still working on it,"},{"time":539000,"text":"because there's still a lot more to do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":542000,"text":"This is Rigoberta Menchu Tum."},{"time":544000,"text":"She also received the Peace Prize."},{"time":546000,"text":"She is now running for president."},{"time":548000,"text":"She is educating the indigenous people of her country"},{"time":551000,"text":"about what it means to be a democracy,"},{"time":554000,"text":"about how you bring democracy to the country,"},{"time":557000,"text":"about educating, about how to vote --"},{"time":559000,"text":"but that democracy is not just about voting;"},{"time":562000,"text":"it's about being an active citizen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":564000,"text":"That's what I got stuck doing --"},{"time":566000,"text":"the landmine campaign."},{"time":568000,"text":"One of the things that made this campaign work"},{"time":571000,"text":"is because we grew from two NGOs"},{"time":574000,"text":"to thousands"},{"time":576000,"text":"in 90 countries around the world,"},{"time":578000,"text":"working together in common cause to ban landmines."},{"time":582000,"text":"Some of the people who worked in our campaign"},{"time":584000,"text":"could only work maybe an hour a month."},{"time":586000,"text":"They could maybe volunteer that much."},{"time":588000,"text":"There were others, like myself,"},{"time":590000,"text":"who were full-time."},{"time":592000,"text":"But it was the actions, together, of all of us"},{"time":595000,"text":"that brought about that change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":597000,"text":"In my view, what we need today"},{"time":599000,"text":"is people getting up"},{"time":601000,"text":"and taking action"},{"time":603000,"text":"to reclaim the meaning of peace."},{"time":605000,"text":"It's not a dirty word."},{"time":607000,"text":"It's hard work every single day."},{"time":609000,"text":"And if each of us"},{"time":611000,"text":"who cares about the different things we care about"},{"time":613000,"text":"got up off our butts"},{"time":615000,"text":"and volunteered"},{"time":617000,"text":"as much time as we could,"},{"time":620000,"text":"we would change this world,"},{"time":622000,"text":"we would save this world."},{"time":624000,"text":"And we can't wait for the other guy. We have to do it ourselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":626000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":628000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}